data.title: Orlando Cogen LP
data.meta_description: Power plant details for Orlando Cogen LP, a natural gas power plant located in Orlando, FL. View the monthly generation and consumption, generator details, and more for Orlando Cogen LP
data.text:
Orlando Cogen LP is ranked #35 out of 276 power plants in Florida in terms of total annual net electricity generation.

Orlando Cogen LP is comprised of 1 generator and generated 349.1 GWh during the 3-month period between September 2023 to December 2023.
